 85→    /**
 86→     * A flag that determines if the SchedulingStates in CurrentQueueState are
 87→     * safe to persist in the database when answering a card. This is used to
 88→     * ensure that the custom JS scheduler has persisted its SchedulingStates
 89→     * back to the Reviewer before we save it to the database. If the custom
 90→     * scheduler has not been configured, then it is safe to immediately set
 91→     * this to true.
 92→     *
 93→     * This flag should be set to false when we show the front of the card
 94→     * and only set to true once we know the custom scheduler has finished its
 95→     * execution, or set to true immediately if the custom scheduler has not
 96→     * been configured.
